            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有关崔浩、《崔氏食经》这两篇很不错哦！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="143556488">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-143556488" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-143556488" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="143556488">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chiyocoffin/">陆秋槎</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2009-10-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">简单易懂的现代史学</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1112250532">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1112250532" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1112250532" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1112250532">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hankun119/">寒鲲</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-11-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一部文笔近人的北魏文化史著作，优在维度全面、史料充分，缺在多有重复、深度不足。不过以作者的文笔，倒不失为一部有深度的入门书。各篇论文之间虽能串联起一定的架构，却没有深入到书名背后应有的深度。虽然不失为一部九十年代的典范式文化史著作，但并没有达到一代史学经典的高度。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="970893245">
